        <span id="BookReviewTitle" class="BookReviewTitle">The Wisdom of Crowds: Why the Many Are Smarter Than the Few and How Collective Wisdom Shapes Business, Economies, Societies and Nations</span>
        <div class="ItemDetail">By
          <span id="Authors">James Surowiecki</span></div>
